    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Abstract class to define a connection manager interface</para>
<para>This is a class whos purpose is to provide an abstraction from underlying network system calls. It must provide a non-blocking upd style send recv interface. When adding a connection it should return a unique int ID for the connection to be referred to by in future interactions with the manager. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
